        <headline>Heat Advisory issued September 3 at 10:42AM MDT until September 4 at 12:00AM MDT by NWS Missoula MT</headline>
        <description>* WHAT...Extreme risk of heat effects.

* WHERE...Lower Hells Canyon/Salmon River Region and
Orofino/Grangeville Region.

* WHEN...Until 11 PM PDT this evening.

* IMPACTS...This level of rare and/or long duration extreme heat
with little to no overnight relief affects anyone without
effective cooling and/or adequate hydration. Impacts likely in
most health systems, heat-sensitive industries and infrastructure.
</description>
        <instruction>Drink plenty of fluids, stay in an air-conditioned room, stay out of
the sun, and check up on relatives and neighbors.</instruction>
